<p>Centre for Soldiers Wives &amp; Mothers<br/>27.6.16.</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton<br/>Can you give some immediate assistance to Mrs. Lilley until we can get her military pay for her which is coming from West-Australia &ndash; She had &pound;1 from you about 3 wks ago</p>
<p>Yours truly<br/>E. H. Bennie.</p>
